# Environment Configuration Examples

## Backend .env Template

```
# Flask Configuration
FLASK_ENV=development
FLASK_HOST=0.0.0.0
FLASK_PORT=5000

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/kuccps_career_hub

# OTP Configuration
OTP_EXPIRY_MINUTES=5
OTP_MAX_ATTEMPTS=3

# SMS Gateway (Twilio)
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your_twilio_account_sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_twilio_auth_token
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890

# Alternative: Africa's Talking
AFRICAS_TALKING_API_KEY=your_africas_talking_key
AFRICAS_TALKING_USERNAME=your_africas_talking_username

# CORS Configuration
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,https://kuccpscareerhub.vercel.app

# Security
JWT_SECRET_KEY=2025
SESSION_SECRET=your-session-secret-key
```

## Frontend .env Template

```
# API Configuration
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

# For Production
# REACT_APP_API_URL=https://api.kuccpscareerhub.dev/api

# Environment
REACT_APP_ENV=development
```

## Database Setup

```bash
# Create PostgreSQL database
createdb kuccps_career_hub

# Load schema
psql -U postgres -d kuccps_career_hub -f database/schema.sql

# Load sample data
psql -U postgres -d kuccps_career_hub -f database/seed_data.sql
```

## Service Configuration

### Twilio Setup (for SMS OTP)
1. Create account at https://www.twilio.com
2. Get Account SID and Auth Token from Console
3. Get or purchase a phone number
4. Add to .env file

### Africa's Talking Setup
1. Create account at https://africastalking.com
2. Get API Key and Username
3. Add to .env file

## Running Locally

### Backend
```bash
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
python app.py
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
```

### Database
```bash
# Start PostgreSQL
psql -U postgres

# Create database
CREATE DATABASE kuccps_career_hub;

# Switch to database
\c kuccps_career_hub

# Load schema
\i database/schema.sql
\i database/seed_data.sql
```
